| SYSADMIN VAGRANT |

To download the Vagrant Boxes and files:

1. grab a copy of the credentials file in the format

    user <some username>
    password <some password>
    location <http://some location>

2. run:

    $ ./sysadmin-vagrant-dl.sh

3. wait a little

4. start the VMs with

    $ vagrant up puppetmaster
    $ vagrant up node

Requirements:
  - Vagrant 1.2+
  - Virtualbox 4+
